♪It's a promise for the future♪

270
00:15:44,190 --> 00:15:45,910
♪The heartbeat of jade♪

271
00:15:45,910 --> 00:15:48,710
♪Follows the rhythm of the cutting machine♪

272
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:50,230
♪The hot blood of a comeback♪

273
00:15:50,230 --> 00:15:53,070
