274
00:15:53,390 --> 00:15:55,030
♪The moment it begins♪

275
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:57,830
♪Is where dreams and reality meet♪

276
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:59,710
♪The journey of a comeback♪

277
00:15:59,710 --> 00:16:02,630
♪I speak with my strength
