00:16:07,070 --> 00:16:08,710
♪The challenges of growth♪

281
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:11,510
♪I never shrink back
but march forward bravely♪

282
00:16:11,710 --> 00:16:13,310
♪The glory of competition♪

283
00:16:13,310 --> 00:16:16,430
♪Should be fought for with my own hands♪

284
